tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    feedback TEXT,
    rating INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE user_ratings (
    rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    service_id INT,
    rating INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE user_ratings (
    rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    trip_id INT,
    rating_value INT,
    feedback_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE trips (
    trip_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    driver_id INT,
    start_location VARCHAR(255),
    end_location VARCHAR(255),
    trip_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE feedback (
  feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID,
  rating INT,
  comments TEXT,
  recorded_at TIMESTAMP
);
